        <p>An excellent property investment opportunity in the UK, The Triangle is a striking development of 99 apartments overlooking the River Stour and neighbouring Victoria Park in the boom town of Ashford, Kent. Ideally located, directly opposite Ashford’s flagship leisure centre Elwick Place, the development is only a 12-minute walk from Ashford International Station. Choose from studios, one, two and three-bedroomed apartments with river and parkland views. The development is directly connected to the town centre via a footbridge to the north, gaining direct access to Elwick Place and also Ashford College. Every convenience is a short walk away, including Ashford International Station, the town’s major retail centres – including the designer outlet village – and an array of supermarkets. Parking is included with two-and three-bedroom apartments and the development is scheduled for completion in Q1 2023.</p>

        <p>Nearly 30% of households in Ashford comprise just one person and 40% are families with children. 18-39 year olds make up 70% of the tenant age profile in Ashford; working professionals and college students who want to live more centrally in Ashford town centre, close to amenities and transport connections. The rental market looks to be further shaken up by the approval of a £250million major film production hub for streaming giants such as Netflix and Amazon, known as Ashford International Studios.</p>
